                            <comment id="15255595" author="krishnakalyan3" created="Sun, 24 Apr 2016 14:03:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Could someone please advice on how the error should be handled, if its an invalid join type?.  I am assuming it should return an error message like &quot;Incorrect join parameter&quot;, is that okay?.&lt;/p&gt;

